def_cn: 十几岁，青少年时期(指从 13 岁到 19 岁)
def_en: If you are in your teens, you are between thirteen and nineteen years old.

def_cn: 面向青少年的;由青少年完成的
def_en: Teen is used to describe things such as films, magazines, bands, or activities that are aimed at or are done by people who are in their teens.

def_cn: 青少年,十几岁的孩子(指从 13 岁到 19 岁)
def_en: A teen is someone aged between thirteen and nineteen years old.
